      "quoted_text": "Stress test #3 \u2014 Leave-one-out. Removes one MBD4-LOF line at a time and re-runs the primary endpoint (rationale: a single highly-sensitive line could drive the n=14 result). Result: 14/14 iterations remain significant. max p=0.0452, min p=0.0082, all",
